$2^{64} \equiv 2^{64 \mod \phi(641)} \pmod{641}$. Since 641 is prime, $\phi(641) = 640$. $64 \equiv 64 \pmod{640}$. So $2^{64} \equiv 2^{64} \pmod{641}$. 

