$2^{60} \equiv 516 \cdot 61 = 31476 \equiv 31476 - 49 \cdot 641 = 31476 - 31409 = 67 \pmod{641}$
$2^{64} = 2^{60} \cdot 2^4 \equiv 67 \cdot 16 = 1072 \equiv 1072 - 641 = 431 \pmod{641}$
